Human Language: english
>Description:
A list-box% is misbehaving with both 'multiple or 'extended.
In both cases it is impossible to navigate through the list:
With 'multiple -- moving up/down with ctrl should move the
selected position but not choose anything, and in both cases
space should toggle the current item.

Currently, it looks like it is impossible to even write that
does that, since there is no way to tell which item has the
focus (only whuch ones are selected).
